author: bsunanda
body: All GEM related files are stored in data/PhaseII. 2 versions of GE11: TP_BaseLine, TDR_BaseLine; 4 versions of GE21: TP_BaseLine, TDR_BaseLine, TDR_10deg, TDR_DEV and 3 versions for ME0: TP_BaseLine, TDR_BaseLine and TDR_Dev
title: bsunanda:Phase2-gem16 Remove and reorder xml files related to GEM
